	(207, 102, 'Cleave', 'When Tandros Kreel attacks an adjacent figure, you may choose one Squad figure that is also adjacent to Tandros Kreel. If the defending figure recieves any wounds from Tandros Kreel''s attack, the chosen figure recieves one wound.'),
