	(241, 118, 'Knockback 14', 'When a small or meduim figure rolls defense dice and is not destroyed by a normal or special attack from Shurrak, immediately roll the 20-sided die. If you roll a 14 or higher, you may Knockback that figure by placing it on any empty space within 3 clear sight spaces of Shurrak. The space must be on the same level as or lower than its current location. A figure moved by Knockback never takes any leaving engagement attack. A non-flying figure moved lower by Knockback can recieve any falling damage that may apply.'),
	(242, 118, 'Lava Resistant', 'Shurrak never rolls for molten lava damage or lava field damage, and he does not have to stop on molten lava spaces.'),
