	(265, 129, 'DUST-OF-DEATH', 'After moving and before attacking, you may either: • Roll the 20-sided die once for each figure adjacent to Red Skull, or • Roll the 20-sided die once for any one figure up to 3 clear sight spaces away If you roll a 19 or higher, that figure is destroyed.'),
	(266, 130, 'Iskra''s Summoning', 'Rechets of Bogdan do not start the game on the battlefield. They must be summoned onto the battlefield by Iskra Esenwein.'),
	(267, 130, 'Lethal Sting', 'When rolling attack dice against a small or medium figure, if a Rechet of Bogdan rolls a skull on every die, the defending figure cannot roll any defense dice and is immediately destroyed.'),
