	(655, 294, 'QUIVERING PALM', 'Start the game with 3 Palm Markers on this card. After moving and before attacking, you may choose a small or medium Unique Hero adjacent to Chen Tang without any Palm Markers on its Army Card. Roll the 20-sided die. If you roll a 13 or higher, place a Palm Marker on the chosen figure’s Army Card. For the duration of the game, at the end of each round, each other figure with one of your Palm Markers on its card receives a wound. Palm Markers cannot be placed on Monk Army Cards.'),
